spec_data.Name: rubygem-ruby2ruby
spec_data.Description:
ruby2ruby provides a means of generating pure ruby code easily from
RubyParser compatible Sexps. This makes making dynamic language
processors in ruby easier than ever!
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 05:23:00 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Generate pure ruby from RubyParser compatible Sexps
